So yea...a good amount of shit has been going on lately, hopefully i can remember everything.  But first, 2 things...

Number one: I'M NOT IN JAIL! We called the court on wednesday and talked to my probation dude who said he doesn't want to put me in jail so i scrounged up 100 bucks to mail to him, and even though the entire 1080 bucks was due in FEB. of this year, and it's already 4 months late, dude said he'd give me ANOTHER year to pay my fines off, do i have the best fucking luck or what? Second...MY MOTHERFUCKING BIRTHDAY IS THURSDAY, JUNE 23RD, WHATCHALL GETTIN ME?

OK now...First, We'll talk about the  GOOD SHIT:

First off, I met this chick last weekend...she rocks, whoa...does she. But we've only hung out once cuz she's always busy or never able to get outta the house which totally blows. I'd definately like to kick it with her alot more cuz as i said, she rules... hopefully she's gonna come to the bar b q with us tomorrow, if not...i dunno. Maybe if she wasn't running cars into the back of old ladies she'd be able to hang out more, eh?

Ooooh......Me and moe are going to michigan during the time the gathering is going on, and probably at LEAST a couple days afterwards, i'm doing a guest spot as a piercer for a good friend of mine while she goes to the gathering. I'm not sure how long after she gets back we're going to stay but i'm kinda hoping it's a little bit at least, everytime i talk to said person i enjoy her and her ""company"" more and more, we'll see what happens with that i guess

Moe and I started working on a new song the other day and ooh wee is it bad ass, we've got the bass, lead , and rhythm lines figured out completely for verse and prechorus/bridge...we just gotta get the chorus worked out on it which i'm sure wont take long.
Cooked out today, me moe and mercy had 6 huge fuckin steaks all to ourselves, we were all stuffed like whoa by the time we finished, it ruled

And now the bad shit...I really fucking miss someone and there's nothing i can really do about it, not as if she'd give a shit anyways but yea, it's been bothering the FUCK out of me the past 2 days seeing Moe and Mercy hangin all over each other and me sittin there by myself, majorly fucking gay. I'm happy that Moe found a chick he's really into but at the same time it just reminds me that i have no one and it makes me all shitty, Oh well...karma's a bitch, i'll have my time soon enough

Amber's not allowed to talk to me anymore, i guess something i said as a joke in her live jounal pissed ogar off and he said he doesn't want her talking to me anymore. It's not like we talk that much anymore anyways, but it still sucks cuz it's nice to hear from my little one every once in a while.

My laptop and cell phone dissapeared from the shop last week, but we know who stole them, or who was involved in stealing them rather, i don't really give a shit about the laptop other than the fact that i had alotta guitar shit on there that i need/want but the fact that he took my phone is some hoe ass shit, all my fucking phone numbers are GONE, i never remember anyone's phone number anymore so i'm royally fucked on that tip. But like i said, karma's a motherfuckin bitch, and i'ma fuck his shit up when i see him, and then let the bounty hunter's loose on his ass, fucking chickenhead junkie motherfucker...you'll get yours, bet on that shit.

I'm growing more and more tired of columbus, i've realized there is nothing here for me anymore and i gotta get the fuck out of here, i've been slowly but surely going apeshit from boredom and the only release i have lately is my music and drugs, and the drugs ain't good for me so i gotta do something to get away from all this shit...i just don't know what, hopefully the michigan trip will open a new window for me and everything will start to go well, who knows."

event,"So yea...Shits been pretty good lately, i been running to try and lose weight, i was on the phone last night and didn't realize how much i walked and ended up walking about 8 miles, after i got off the phone i ran another 2, for some reason i didn't get tired at all, my feet didn't hurt or anything. The only reason i stopped was because my ribs started hurting all of a sudden and my lungs were burning, so i figured that would be a good time to stop.
I got 100 Bucks from my grandfather to go towards my fines today, so hopefully i'll have my liscence back ASAP...I also got my ""A Dozen Black Roses"" Book that D' bought me from amazon <333

I think that's pretty much all that's been going on lately, i been busting my ass trying to find a job but nothing's happened with that yet, my grandfather might get me a job at the post office sorting mail at night making like 10 bucks an hour, but who knows.

I decided to throw this behind a cut, because i feel like...anyone that wants to read it, will read it anyways even if it's behind a cut, and everyone that doesn't can just scroll past my entry like i do with half of my friends page.

event,"
Your wings are BROKEN and tattered. You are
an angelic spirit who has fallen from grace for
one reason or another - possibly, you made one
tragic mistake that cost you everything. Or
maybe you were blamed for a crime you didn't
commit. In any case, you are faithless and
joyless. You find no happiness, love, or
acceptance in your love or in yourself. Most
days are a burden and you wonder when the
hurting will end. Sweet, beautiful and
sorrowful, you paint a tragic and touching
picture. You are the one that few understand.
Those that do know you are likely to love you
deeply and wish that they could do something to
ease your pain. You are constantly living in
memories of better times and a better world.
You are hard on yourself and self-critical or
self-loathing. Feeling rejected and unloved,
you are sensitive, caring, deep, and despite
your tainted nature, your soul is
breathtakingly beautiful.

Pretty much sums up what i've been feelin like lately, i dunno what the fuck has been going on. I lost one of the people i care about the most because i had no way of getting ahold of her, but it's still my fault, everything is always my fault, i've accepted that fact.

Let's see...what's been going on lately...after i got out of jail i went on a couple coke binges for days on end, and after someone refused to talk to me and let me explain what's been going on i did a half ounce in about 3 days...drowned my sorrows, as it were. I just wish you would talk to me and understand why i didn't want to bring you down with me and make you upset by dealing with my bullshit, but it's too late i guess.

I got kicked out of the house, i'm staying at my grandparents until friday, they wont let me stay any longer, hopefully i can find a place by then, if not i'll either be on the streets or in a shelter, i'm thinking about jacking a car and hauling ass to new york, since there's nothing left for me down here. On the up side...i got my GED diploma in the mail today, which means i could start school in the summer, not as if it matters since i wont have a place to stay or any way to get to school.
I been writing alot of lyrics and shit lately, maybe i'll decide to post something up here, or even write something new, who knows
